[head=1]Captain Impeachment[/head][/color]
[color=Grey]This form is to criminally charge the Captain to remove them from office.[/color]

[bold]Captain:[/bold]
               ‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾
